data.enText: a building where large quantities of goods are stored, especially before they are sent to shops/stores to be sold

word_means: 把…存入仓库；把…存入保税仓库

means: 把…存入仓库；把…存入保税仓库

tr: a storehouse for goods and merchandise

value.def: A warehouse is a large building where raw materials or manufactured goods are stored until they are exported to other countries or distributed to shops to be sold.

trans: 数据仓库(汇集企业各部门信息的大量数据)
